## Project Board

Roadmap work is tracked on the [GitHub Project](https://github.com/users/colin-gourlay/projects/3). See [wiki/Project-Board.md](wiki/Project-Board.md) for:

- The configured views (Board by Status, Table by Area, Public Visibility Focus)
- Definitions for the Area, Impact, and Target Month fields
- Conventions for draft items vs issues
- How to convert discussion outcomes into tracked work
